#

Pumpkin Feta Salad

45 min
$10
250 kcal
Difficulty: 30%
Servings: 4

Allergens:

Dairy

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianGluten-Free

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Main

Tags:

SaladHealthyEasy

Description

A warm and hearty salad featuring roasted pumpkin, creamy feta, and a mix of fresh greens, drizzled with a light vinaigrette.

Ingredients

  • pumpkin: 2 cups, cubed
  • feta cheese: 1/2 cup, crumbled
  • mixed salad greens: 4 cups
  • olive oil: 2 tablespoons
  • balsamic vinegar: 1 tablespoon
  • honey: 1 teaspoon
  • salt: to taste
  • black pepper: to taste
